snippet.title: Sonic Frontiers Knuckles Reveal Teaser
snippet.description:
Knuckles was teased today in Sonic Frontiers, as well as a short exclusive gameplay clip of Sonic in the game during the Sonic Central.

#Sonic #Knuckles #sonicthehedgehog
